The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Bengal | Jawan caught
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   Jawan caught
                            
	Siliguri, Nov. 17: An allegedly drunk BSF jawan strayed into Bangladesh and shot dead three persons before being de-tained by BDR personnel.         
	BDR said it caught R.P. Singh drunk off North Dinajpur.         
	PTI quoted BSF officer K. Srinivasan as saying: A flag meeting was held where the BSF apologised for the unfortunate incident...                                                                                                                                                                          
